    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Melody pipes on bagpipes; they may be of conical or cylindrical bore and be fitted with either a single or a double reed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
